OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNext boss says UK needs    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmore foreign workers       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The chief executive of High Street     
OL,6, chain Next is urging the government to 
OL,7, let more foreign workers into the UK to
OL,8, alleviate chronic labour shortages.    
OL,10,FLord Wolfson, who was a prominent      
OL,11,Fadvocate of Brexit, said the UK's      
OL,12,Fcurrent immigration policy was         
OL,13,Fcrippling economic growth.             
OL,15,FHe said firms should pay a tax to      
OL,16,Femploy foreign workers, to encourage   
OL,17,Fthem to recruit from the UK first.     
OL,19,FThe Home Office was approached for     
OL,20,Fcomment.                               
